                "key": "Capolavoro incompleto",
                "string_values": [
                  "<p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">Quando usa un'</span><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">abilità elementale</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">, il personaggio riceve un </span><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">bonus DAN per tutti gli elementi</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\"> pari a un</span><span style=\"color: #37FFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">8%/10%/12%/14%/16%</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\"> per </span><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">15 s</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\"> e un </span><span style=\"color: #CCBFAD\">Legame vitale</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\"> pari a un </span><span style=\"color: #37FFFF\">24%</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\"> dei </span><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">PS max</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">. Quest'effetto può attivarsi una volta ogni </span><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">10 s</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">. Quando il </span><span style=\"color: #CCBFAD\">Legame vitale</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\"> si dissolve, per ogni 1.000 </span><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">PS</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\"> dissolti il personaggio ottiene un </span><span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">2%/2.5%/3%/3.5%/4%</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\"> di </span><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">bonus DAN per tutti gli elementi</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">, fino a un </span><span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">12%/15%/18%/21%/24%</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\"> massimo. Questo effetto dura </span><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">15 s</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">.</span></p>"
